OL,6,FA woman who defrauded a junior school
OL,7,Fhas been ordered to pay back almost
OL,8,F#75,000.
OL,10,FJoanne Anderson of Summerhill, East
OL,11,FHerrington, in Sunderland, had
OL,12,Fpreviously been handed a two-year
OL,13,Fprison sentence, suspended for two
OL,14,Fyears, after pleading guilty to fraud
OL,15,Fby false representation in 2023.
OL,17,FThe 52-year-old had worked at Fulwell
OL,18,FJunior School, , for around 20 years
OL,19,Fand was responsible for managing the
OL,20,Ffinancial budget.
