OL,6,FBetween 2017 and 2021, Anderson forged
OL,7,Fthe signatures of senior staff on at
OL,8,Fleast 409 cheques, which were made
OL,9,Fpayable to herself.
OL,11,FHowever, a police investigation was
OL,12,Flaunched after an auditor noticed a
OL,13,Fdiscrepancy in the transactions.
OL,15,FFollowing her sentencing, financial
OL,16,Finvestigators began compiling records
OL,17,Fof Anderson's earnings from crime and
OL,18,Fher current assets.
