OL,6,FShe appeared at on Friday 16 February,
OL,7,Fwhere a judge granted a confiscation
OL,8,Forder to retrieve #41,475 taken
OL,9,Fthrough fraudulent activity.
OL,11,FAn amount of #33,315.00 has already
OL,12,Fbeen recovered from Anderson's pension.
OL,14,FDetective Inspector Phil Thoburn, of
OL,15,FNorthumbria Police, said: "This is a
OL,16,Fgood result for us and the school
OL,17,Fafter what has been a difficult time
OL,18,Ffor staff and children.
