OL,6,F"In this case, Anderson took advantage
OL,7,Fof being a trusted member of staff and
OL,8,Fdefrauded her employer out of almost
OL,9,F#120,000.
OL,11,F"However, she now has a criminal
OL,12,Frecord, is serving a suspended
OL,13,Fsentence, and thanks to the Proceeds
OL,14,Fof Crime Act, will pay back a
OL,15,Fsignificant amount of her ill-gotten
OL,16,Fgains.
OL,18,F"The community which the school serves
OL,19,Fdeserves to see action like this being
OL,20,Ftaken.
